{"word":"ἀλγίων","slug":"ἀλγίων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n3902\" key=\"a)lgi/wn\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀλγ-ίων</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἄλγιστος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">η</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, irreg. <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Comp.\">Comp.</a></gram> </gramGrp> and <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\">Sup. of</gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλγεινός</foreign>, formed fr. <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Subst.\">Subst.</a></pos> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄλγος</foreign> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καλλίων, αἰσχίων</foreign>): —<sense id=\"n3902.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">more</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">most painful, grievous</tr_>, or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">distressing</tr_>: — of <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Comp.\">Comp.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> has only neut. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄλγιον</foreign>, in signf. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">so much the worse</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῷ δ᾽ ἄλγιον, αἴ κ᾽ ἐθέλῃσιν . . ἄμμι μάχεσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:278\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></